<p>Here&#8217;s a link to the Bloomberg report on the German concessions to Ireland and Merkle&#8217;s willingness to relent on the Deutsch bond bomb: <a href="http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-28/ireland-wins-eu85-billion-aid-germany-drops-threat-on-bonds.html">http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-28/ireland-wins-eu85-billion-aid-germany-drops-threat-on-bonds.html</a></p>
